{"tid":1973695,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"最港最好食嘅日式同南洋咖喱","createTime":"2020-04-15T10:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T11:36:25.000Z","uid":228263,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a3e0713ac5121eba0290d36be68f2df02abb656e","tid":1973695,"uid":228263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T10:40:51.000Z","msg":"求推薦<br />\n有冇好食嘅黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日式咖喱<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pUwf3vq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpUwf3vq.jpg&h=2340a595&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本咖哩一般不太辣，因為加入了濃縮果泥，所以甜味較重。雖然日式咖哩又稱歐風咖哩，事實上還是由日本人所發明的。之所以稱歐風咖哩，是因為其所用的稠化物為法國菜常用的奶油炒麵糊（roux），多用來製作濃湯，而且香料取材也多傾向南印度風格。歐風咖哩雖然較為濃醇，但與印度相似料理比較起來，香料味還是明顯不及。咖哩除了可以伴飯吃外，還可以作為拉麵和烏龍麵等湯麵類食物的湯底，這方面和其他地方的咖哩有較大分別。北海道札幌地區還有湯咖哩以及白咖哩。<br />\n<br />\n咖哩在明治時代由英國人傳進日本之後，與日本的米食文化結合，香滑濃稠的咖哩飯深受日本人的喜愛，家家戶戶的餐桌上幾乎都可見咖哩的蹤跡，堪稱為日本的國民美食。之後又演化出各式獨具特色的料理。<br />\nSource:<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/咖哩#日本\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E5%92%96%E5%93%A9%23%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQPuvrtn4HlyTxFQ%2BxjLCx7s%3D&h=50b74122\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/咖哩#日本</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n南洋咖喱<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d9HZLJS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd9HZLJS.jpg&h=f8ce8d11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南洋咖哩源於馬來西亞、新加坡、印尼，早期定居在麻六甲、印尼和新加坡一帶的華人移民後裔，與馬來人通婚、結合的飲食文化結晶，就被稱為娘惹，最具代表性的料理如叻沙(Laksa)，是馬來與新加坡都有的風味飲食。 <br />\nKawan香料廚房主廚王姵懿嫻熟馬來風味的掌握。<br />\nKawan香料廚房主廚王姵懿嫻熟馬來風味的掌握。<br />\n<br />\n南洋咖哩在當地又可分為馬來華人、印度、娘惹與正宗馬來味，台灣的南洋咖哩則以馬來華人的風味居多。主打新加坡料理、大姊的店主廚黃菁蓮說：「南洋咖哩用根莖類辛香料的比重比印度咖哩高，如薑黃、馬鈴薯等，且一定會加上椰漿收尾。」 <br />\nSource:<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/lifestyle/daily/20151211/36947324/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fdaily%2F20151211%2F36947324%2F&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQPuvrtn4HlyTxFQ%2BxjLCx7s%3D&h=24522440\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fdaily%2F20151211%2F36947324%2F&h=5b69c2c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/lifestyle/daily/20151211/36947324/</a>"},{"pid":"b4681598655f03bad61cec1038ecd1a8d92655e4","tid":1973695,"uid":133743,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T10:44:16.000Z","msg":"日式咖哩真係好好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n次次去日本都要食兩碟<br />\n香港除左灣仔間cat&rsquo;s eye仲有咩推介？"},{"pid":"c1d8a5e8b2af5ef607869adae85c0da2d7f0dcd1","tid":1973695,"uid":71508,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T10:45:02.000Z","msg":"日式咖哩=銀咖哩<br />\n南洋咖哩=大快活"},{"pid":"66c9373aebec7960af10c6ecb7915fa72024eff1","tid":1973695,"uid":130197,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4681598655f03bad61cec1038ecd1a8d92655e4","tid":1973695,"uid":133743,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T10:44:16.000Z","msg":"日式咖哩真係好好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n次次去日本都要食兩碟<br />\n香港除左灣仔間cat&rsquo;s eye仲有咩推介？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T10:45:28.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣world trade對面有間都幾好味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73ee434df447d6a65e08c8a9f2737606ebb6087","tid":1973695,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T10:46:08.000Z","msg":"南洋北角  杜文澤介紹有間黃店"},{"pid":"8d9651d0e78c2d33ca06face01271e416f16cf83","tid":1973695,"uid":133743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"66c9373aebec7960af10c6ecb7915fa72024eff1","tid":1973695,"uid":130197,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4681598655f03bad61cec1038ecd1a8d92655e4","tid":1973695,"uid":133743,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T10:44:16.000Z","msg":"日式咖哩真係好好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n次次去日本都要食兩碟<br />\n香港除左灣仔間cat&rsq